OL,3,CGovernment to fund private colleges
OL,4,Cper pupil rather than lump sum
OL,6,FGuernsey's three private colleges will
OL,7,Fstill get taxpayer funding but on a
OL,8,Fper-pupil basis, rather than the
OL,9,Fcurrent arrangement which sees them
OL,10,Freceive a lump sum each academic year.
OL,12,FThe island's Education Committee
OL,13,Fpreviously announced plans to scrap
OL,14,Fthe grant, which currently stands at
OL,15,Faround #3 million, while the schools
OL,16,Fwanted to increase it.
