OL,3,CGovernment to fund private colleges
OL,4,Cper pupil rather than lump sum
OL,6,FFollowing a debate in Guernsey States
OL,7,Fand Deputy Gavin St Pier's successful
OL,8,Famendment, it was decided that annual
OL,9,Fgovernment financial support would
OL,10,Fcontinue with the amount based on the
OL,11,Fnumber of enrolled students.
OL,13,FSpeaking ahead of the vote, Deputy St
OL,14,FPier said, "It's about providing
OL,15,Freasonable balance" and not exposing
OL,16,Fthe taxpayer to "unacceptable risk".
OL,18,FThe changes will come into effect from
OL,19,Fthe 2025-26 academic year on a rolling
OL,20,Fbasis and be adjusted for inflation.
