OL,3,CGovernment to fund private colleges
OL,4,Cper pupil rather than lump sum
OL,6,FThe funding model can only be reduced
OL,7,For withdrawn with approval from the
OL,8,FStates and five years' notice to the
OL,9,FColleges.
OL,11,FThere were concerns that had the
OL,12,Ffunding not been renewed in some form,
OL,13,Fparents would face higher fees and
OL,14,Fthere would be fewer bursary places.
OL,16,FIn a joint statement, Blanchelande
OL,17,FCollege, Elizabeth College and The
OL,18,FLadies' College said they are
OL,19,F"relieved".
