OL,7,FDeputies for seeing the valuable role
OL,8,Fthe Colleges play in the Bailiwick's
OL,9,Feducational landscape, island-wide
OL,10,Fcommunity and economy.
OL,12,F"We would also like to acknowledge the
OL,13,Fhigh level of political, parent and
OL,14,Fpublic engagement in this important
OL,15,Fdebate and the significant support we
OL,16,Fhave received from the business sector
OL,17,Fand other stakeholders."
